<section id="fs-idm24204016" class="free-response">
<title>Free Response</title>
<exercise id="fs-idm24024624">
<problem id="fs-idp25798256">
<para id="fs-idp64733536">Explain the reason why the imprudent and excessive use of antibiotics has resulted in a major global problem.</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp40969120">
<label/>
<para id="fs-idp11035472">Antibiotics kill bacteria that are sensitive to them; thus, only the resistant ones will survive. These resistant bacteria will reproduce, and therefore, after a while, there will be only resistant bacteria.</para>
</solution>
