<exercise id="fs-idp48620288">
<problem id="fs-idm111624560">
<para id="fs-idp81416160">Researchers have discovered that washing spinach with water several times does not prevent foodborne diseases due to <emphasis effect="italics">E. coli</emphasis>. How can you explain this fact?</para>
